{"tid":2000614,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(高層震怒?) 香港殯儀館塌天花　職員稱內部裝修","createTime":"2020-05-04T03:52:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T04:00:52.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cda227bb0364a809645717ca0a518ad3fbbc6ea1","tid":2000614,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T03:52:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200504/s00001/a94da7b7f50caaa7b7b8eea41793c2cc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200504%2Fs00001%2Fa94da7b7f50caaa7b7b8eea41793c2cc.jpg&h=187472e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（facebook專頁「賣棺材的男孩」圖片）<br />\n<br />\n網上流傳一張相片，稱一間位於港島區的殯儀館發生塌天花事件，據悉涉事殯儀館為北角香港殯儀館，事件中無人受傷。香港殯儀館回覆本報稱沒有發生塌天花事件，僅曾內部裝修。<br />\n<br />\n根據facebook專頁「賣棺材的男孩」昨晚（3日）上載的相片，香港殯儀館地下大堂位置昨日曾有一幅假天花倒塌，天花連同鋼筋墜落於大堂地下近接待處位置。本報翻查資料圖片，顯示該假天花上曾掛有一棧大型水晶吊燈，未知該吊燈有否同時被毁。<br />\n<br />\n據悉事件中無人受傷，警方及消防處均沒有接獲相關報案，殯儀館服務沒有受影響。<br />\n<br />\n記者今早致電香港殯儀館了解，接線職員稱殯儀館沒有發生塌天花事件，該相片實為內部裝修圖片。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200504/s00001/1588561174923/%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%AE%AF%E5%84%80%E9%A4%A8%E5%A1%8C%E5%A4%A9%E8%8A%B1-%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E7%A8%B1%E5%85%A7%E9%83%A8%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200504%2Fs00001%2F1588561174923%2F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%2582%25B3%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25AE%25AF%25E5%2584%2580%25E9%25A4%25A8%25E5%25A1%258C%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E8%258A%25B1-%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E5%2585%25A7%25E9%2583%25A8%25E8%25A3%259D%25E4%25BF%25AE&d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWX4kJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=ea6a53d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200504%2Fs00001%2F1588561174923%2F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%2582%25B3%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25AE%25AF%25E5%2584%2580%25E9%25A4%25A8%25E5%25A1%258C%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E8%258A%25B1-%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E5%2585%25A7%25E9%2583%25A8%25E8%25A3%259D%25E4%25BF%25AE&h=93b45150\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200504/s00001/1588561174923/%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%AE%AF%E5%84%80%E9%A4%A8%E5%A1%8C%E5%A4%A9%E8%8A%B1-%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E7%A8%B1%E5%85%A7%E9%83%A8%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE</a>"},{"pid":"c14d8ec90d29b1c52273156b867d9a58b44e6177","tid":2000614,"uid":37111,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T03:58:34.000Z","msg":"咁都冇發生係咪想推做靈異事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b33ef1fcca53284fab09b41bd895d95e088369de","tid":2000614,"uid":25169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T03:58:49.000Z","msg":"唔用梯都拆到落黎，蜘蛛俠轉左行咩"},{"pid":"c8c0fa28dfeda45ba17e0c56d7201ffea52e1f22","tid":2000614,"uid":202051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係唔係有冤死者"}]}